    <title>Samsung DCS Telephone System (Emmarentia Premises)</title>
    <para>
        In July 2005 a Samsung DCS telephone system was installed to replace the Telkom Jupiter system.
        This system has is simpler and more programmable, and offers better integration with other
        systems such as the gate, answering machine, etc.
    </para>

    <section>
      <title>Lines</title>
      <para>
        We have 3 incoming lines. 2 are used for telephone, one for the fax machine. All three lines are available as 
	outgoing lines. he fax machine line will be used last.
      </para>
    </section>  
    
