    <section>
        <title>Putting a line on hold</title>
        <para>
            This functionality is only available from the switchboard or conference phone. Hold on extensions simply mutes the line.
            Press <literal><![CDATA[lineX]]></literal> to take incoming call on that line. 
            Press <literal><![CDATA[lineY]]></literal> to switch to that line.
        </para>
    </section>

    <section>
        <title>Conference calls</title>
        <para>
            Conference calls can be set up only from the switch board or the conference phone.
        </para>
        <para>
            <orderedlist>
                <listitem><para>
                   Phone outside party.        
                </para></listitem>
                <listitem><para>
                    Let them know you are getting somebody to join the conversation.
                </para></listitem>
                <listitem><para>
                    Press <literal><![CDATA[<conference]]></literal> and either
                    <itemizedlist>
                        <listitem><para>
                            dial the extension no to join, or
                        </para></listitem>
                        <listitem><para>
                            dial an external line no.
                        </para></listitem>
                    </itemizedlist>
                </para></listitem>
                <listitem><para>
                   Press top right soft key (just below screen) twice to establish conference call.                     
                </para></listitem>
            </orderedlist>
        </para>
    </section>
    
    <section>
        <title>Night mode</title>
        <para>
            The night mode will
            <itemizedlist>
                <listitem><para>
                    transfer the rings to all extensions,
                </para></listitem>
                <listitem><para>
                    let the answering machine pick up after 5 rings if call not taken.
                </para></listitem>
            </itemizedlist>
        </para>
        <para>
            To set night/day mode, press the <literal><![CDATA[Mode]]></literal> key, enter the password (0000), and select
            night or day.
        </para>
    </section>
